             TO  RJL0127-CA-SCURTY-ECLUD-AMT

      *@    CA담보환산금액
           MOVE  WK-H-O1-CA-SCURTY-AUC
             TO  RJL0127-CA-SCURTY-AUC

170629*@ 원만기환산율 = 만기년월일 - 신규년월일
      *@                  1년이하（２０％），１년초과（５０％）

           IF  WK-H-01-EXPIR-YMD = ( '99991231' OR '        ' )
      *@만기년월일＝＇９９９９１２３１＇ OR ' ' 원만기환산율＝５０％

              MOVE  CO-NUM-50
                TO  WK-RMAIN-EXPIR-URCRT
           ELSE
               PERFORM  S6000-XCJIIL01-CALL-RTN
                  THRU  S6000-XCJIIL01-CALL-EXT
           END-IF


      *@신용공여한도= CA담보환산금액
170413*@     + (MAX(SUM(BS기준한도)-SUM(BS기준잔액),0)
      *@     *원만기환산율)
      *@   원만기환산율: 1년이하（２０％），１년초과（５０％）
           COMPUTE  WK-H-O1-GRCR-CLAM
                 =  WK-H-O1-CA-SCURTY-AUC
                 + ( FUNCTION MAX(WK-H-O1-GRCR-CLAM, 0)
                 *   WK-RMAIN-EXPIR-URCRT / 100 )

           MOVE  WK-H-O1-GRCR-CLAM
             TO  RJL0127-GRCR-CLAM

      *@외화신용공여대상이면　외화신용공여한도＝신용공여한도
           IF  WK-H-O1-FC-FRCR-GB > 0
               MOVE  WK-H-O1-GRCR-CLAM
                 TO  RJL0127-FC-GRCR-CLAM
           ELSE
               MOVE  ZERO
                 TO  RJL0127-FC-GRCR-CLAM
           END-IF

170413*    BS기준한도
           MOVE WK-H-O1-BS-BASE-CLAM
             TO RJL0127-BS-BASE-CLAM

           #DYDBIO  INSERT-CMD-Y TKJL0127-PK TRJL0127-REC

           EVALUATE  TRUE
               WHEN  COND-DBIO-OK
